I enjoyed Webster went it was on TV. I love it just as much now as I did back then. It is a great family show. The comedy is wonderful. I wished more television comedies were like this.
Webster is back for a fourth season and I can wait to own this set. I already have the first three seasons and now I'm going to add this season to my collection.
